fields.name: equizone_phenybutazone_powder
fields.description: Equizone 100  was the  FIRST FDA approved phenylbutazone powder on the market.  A  palatable bute ( citrus flavored) powder approved for oral use in horses by the FDA.  Equizone 100 and Equizone 50 are  both made from all natural sweetners, no artificial sweetners added.
